prompts.frontCover: A charmingly minimalist 2D cartoon illustration for a birthday card. The entire design is on a clean, solid cream-colored background. In the center, a very long, single strand of spaghetti is artfully draped and looped across the page, forming elegant, simple swirls. A single, tiny, cheerful cartoon meatball with a smiling face is perched right in the middle of the spaghetti tangle. Above the spaghetti, in a beautiful, readable, flowing handwritten cursive script, the words "Hope your birthday" are written. Below the spaghetti, the script continues with "is im-pasta-bly fun!". The illustration uses a limited, warm color palette—just the warm yellow of the pasta and the gentle brown of the meatball. The overall style is flat, clean, and elegantly simple, conveying humor through its clever visual pun.
